description:
13-year-old Yuuki Yuuna joins the Hero Club. Yuuki Yuuna is an ordinary second-year middle school student. She gets up in the morning. She goes to classes, and is now participating in a club formed by Inubouzaki Fuu called "The Hero club". They do community service such as helping other clubs, searching for cats, and doing activities with the pre-schoolers. 

All this changes after the four club members suddenly get frozen in time, and are sent into a mysterious version of their world where they have to battle enemies called "Vertex" who threaten The Divine Tree.
